{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act33side", "eventName": "巴別塔", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "BB-ST-3", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "靈魂盡頭", "storyInfo": "特蕾西婭在博士的記憶中看到了所有，並在最後與那個人完成了告別。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_light", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抹除記憶。對特蕾西婭來說，她亦缺少足夠的經驗。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更不必論，她此刻不得不面對一種她知之甚少的思維。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不知道會遇見什麼，也無法預料是否會帶來危險，但她並沒有退縮的餘地。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這已是她生命最後的決定。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她走在博士的記憶中，無數的記憶被拆解成為絲線消散。"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記憶在消逝。無聲無息。"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她走過了從未見識，也無法認知的世界。"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如此輝煌的文明為何會終結？"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如流星般璀璨的天才們又為何對這個終極問題苦苦求索而無解？"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抵抗是否沒有意義？團結是否只是空想？"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "泰拉的未來是否已然注定？她所愛的家園呢？"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她所愛的人呢？"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她沒有答案。她找不到答案。"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她只能繼續漫步於記憶散去後的虛無。"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "終於，她看到了熟悉的人。"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_rhodescom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_smallsalutecannon", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_smallsalutecannon", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "in"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "in", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cheer_street", "volume": 0.4, "loop": "true", "channel": "c"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "c", "fadetime": 6.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家的熱情讓你無所適從嗎？", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_048"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼來了，凱爾希。", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是慶祝你又一次大勝的慶典，難道我不該到場嗎？", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_048"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道的，我很久沒有……我們那時候，能慶祝的日子不多。", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該如何慶祝，我已經有些生疏了。", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，你會慢慢熟悉的。巴別塔會成為一個新的開始。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#11$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#13$1"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去吧，我們應該好好慶祝一番。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#13$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭看到凱爾希抬手拍了拍博士的後背，輕輕將那人推向等候已久的人群。"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有太多人擠過來了，一雙雙手伸向前，爭先恐後想要同博士握握手，拍拍博士的肩膀。"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有些個子很高的傢伙，膽子很大，竟然直接將手放在博士的腦袋上狠狠揉了揉。"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_048"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……？", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，我替手下的冒失向您道歉，博士，我剛想阻止他……", "name": "Scout"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我的手臂受傷了……根本來不及。", "name": "Scout"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_048"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係……傷勢如何？", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恢復得不錯。", "name": "Scout"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜，今夜有很多飲品你都沒辦法享用了。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1309_1#1$1", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "100,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，博士，我會代這傢伙多喝上幾杯的。", "name": "Ace"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1309_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不是您最後果斷地變招突襲，我們恐怕都要落進包圍網裡。", "name": "Ace"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1309_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來，敬您，我們可得好好喝上幾杯。", "name": "Ace"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1309_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恐怕我的酒量會讓你失望，Ace先生。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "r"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "r", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_050", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓一讓，讓一讓，我都要看不見今天的主角了。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_050"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼多人，我還是第一次覺得這間指揮室這麼小，要不要之後幫你擴建一下啊？外面可還有好多人提著好吃的趕過來呢。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_050"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1072_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，大家都在為您所帶來的勝利而歡呼，但您看上去有些……不自在。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_050"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為自己遮掩得不錯。咳，只是在人群中覺得緊張。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "100,0", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.2}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 1.02, "duration": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿，小心，別往前擠了。阿米婭，你還好嗎？", "name": "Scout"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1311_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1295_1#8$1", "posfrom": "-80,0", "posto": "-80,0", "duration": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒事！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1295_1#8$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士！快和我來，我和特蕾西婭小姐為你準備了烤蛋糕！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1295_1#8$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看，烤箱太燙了，還把我的手指燙了一個水泡。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1295_1#8$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝……呃！這沒事嗎？誰有燙傷膏……", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一聲輕輕的咳嗽響起，人群應聲向兩邊散開。"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "in", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-80,0", "posto": "-200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-150,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭看到了一個身著白裙的女人擦肩而過，笑著向博士伸出一隻手，手上有未愈的針刺傷口。"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是她自己。"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1", "duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_light", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喜悅淡去，記憶淡去，耳邊的聲音淡去。"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭抹除這段自己也無比熟悉的記憶，接著向前走去。"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她看到了一段自己從未在PRTS中看到的記錄。"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_energywell", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "e"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "channel": "e", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_abyss_1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.08, "yScale": 1.08}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_048", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "調用影像功能。啟用管理員權限加密。", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "影像編號<color=#FF4200>（0091_admin）</color>……添加主題：<color=#FF4200>（這是留給你的）</color>。", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啟動記錄……開始錄影。", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_signlntrfrnc", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_signalInterference", "layer": 0.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_oldtv", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_oldtvelectricity", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "o"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我沒有堅持到你醒來，你會看到這段影片。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在一切塵埃落定之前，我會留在這裡，留在最安全的地方。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我做完所有的一切之後，我會在沉默中消失……", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "消失在所有恨我的人面前。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的心中時刻有一個聲音提醒我，拷問我——“我是誰？”", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是我們自身的守望者？還是後來文明的背叛者？", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經無法認清我自己——", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "查看所有我留下的記錄之後，你會得出一個答案。但至少此刻，我已不再猶豫自己該做什麼。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我……", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當你醒來，我應該已經消失在你的過去，不會再出現在我們約定的未來。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我希望……", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……記錄暫停。刪除剛才的所有內容。我……還需要一點時間。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "e", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "o", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_light", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她沒有猶豫，沒有嘆息，只是默默繼續做著該做的事情。"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭越走越深，靠近了埋藏在更深處的回憶。"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "46_g4_rmbtwild_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_churchfire", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "c"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "channel": "c", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.2, "r": 0.92, "g": 0.4, "b": 0.3, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我需要你們聯絡最近的救援隊！失事的運輸隊車輛上有雷姆必拓的標誌，這是你們的隊伍……", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽到裡面還有倖存者的聲音！", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "滋——我們已經聯繫上，但是從最近的採礦地塊趕到現場還需要時間。", "name": "通訊聲"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽您的回報，那裡曾發生過搶劫案，我們同樣要通知武裝安保，讓他們立刻出發。", "name": "通訊聲"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……唔……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……武裝安保……但雷姆必拓對沒有家庭支持的感染者……", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖——", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "c", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_removestone", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "49_i20_1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "堅持一下……我現在就能把你拉出來……", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "千萬不要睡著……嘶……好孩子，把手伸過來。", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抓住！", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可……我……好累……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的名字是什麼——", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我——", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "名字……？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "49_i20_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.1, "yScaleTo": 1.1, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽媽……叫我……阿米婭……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭，堅持一下，抓緊我的手！", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……抓住你了——", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會放手——", "name": "博士"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "c", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記憶破碎。"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡就是特蕾西婭的終點，博士記憶的終點——"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“特蕾西婭……”"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不可能，明明所有的記憶都已經……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“特蕾西婭。”"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她循著聲音，來到了一處虛無之前，聲音從虛無之後傳來。"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡是哪裡——", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "31_g3_mini12_farmland", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2, "y": 70.0, "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_reedmarshes", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "r"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "r", "fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "r", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你終於走到了這裡，我在等你。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士……？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#7$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很少有人會這麼叫我，他們喜歡稱呼我的團隊代號——“預言家”。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……預言家……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#7$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，凱爾希信任的，其實是你。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#7$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很對不起凱爾希。但沒辦法，我確實深陷一個避無可避的陽謀之中。", "name": "預言家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一直在這裡看著你，看著你為希望奔走，看著你為背叛而痛苦——", "name": "預言家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像看著曾經的我自己。", "name": "預言家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……抱歉。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#6$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在的你只是博士情感燃燒後的殘渣，我沒辦法在這樣的情況下，單獨保留下你的情感和記憶……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你已經來到了終點，做你該做的吧。", "name": "預言家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你相信我。", "name": "預言家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……也許有些遲了，不過，很高興見到你。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也很高興見到你，特蕾西婭。", "name": "預言家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hidehaystack", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "s"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "預言家走向了遠方無盡的麥田，消失在其中。"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "氣流肆虐過麥田，嘩嘩作響，空間中最後的景象也崩解四散，直到翻出絲線的盡頭。"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "s", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭牽住它，很快，絲線開始逐漸失去光澤，碎成粉末。"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到了說再見的時候了……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "未來，我們還會再見的吧……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱爾希……阿米婭……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#9$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……{@nickname}。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wind", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_reedmarshes", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "r"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "r", "fadetime": 6.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "BackgroundTween", "attributes": {"yFrom": 70.0, "duration": 6.0, "ease": "OutQuad", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "gridbg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "47_g14_skyovercast_L1/47_g14_skyovercast_R1/47_g14_skyovercast_L2/47_g14_skyovercast_R2", "solidwidth": "1280/1280/1280/1280", "solidheight": "720/720/720/720", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "largebgtween", "attributes": {"duration": 25.0, "yFrom": 720.0, "yTo": 360.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭鬆開了手中最後的線頭，目睹它如星光般散開，消逝。"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她邁開步走去，走向了希望……"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走向了死亡。"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "gridbg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}